25|$|Each {{national}} KPMG firm is {{an independent}} legal entity {{and is a member}} of KPMG International Cooperative, a Swiss entity registered in the Swiss Canton of Zug. KPMG International changed its legal structure from a Swiss Verein to a co-operative under <b>Swiss</b> <b>law</b> in 2003.|$|E
